For CO2-TPD, the catalyst samples (20 mg) were firstly
reduced in 5% H2 in N2 at 20 ml min1 for 2 h at 603 K,
followed by exposure to CO2 at 323 K for 1 h at 20 ml min1.
TPD was performed under H2 flow at 20 ml min1 to study the
